transcripts: Making a healthy lunch can be tricky. but this chicken salad recipe will ensure you always have a nutritious meal on hand. We're going to start with a little bit of celery, a small peice of onion, some Greek yogurt, and some cooked chicken. Attach your cross blade and we're going to use the magic bullet pulsing technique. With this recipe you have a healthy meal any time of the day, and it took just seconds to make.
